---

## Interview Process

1. **Initial Screening** (30 min) - Phone call with recruiter
2. **Technical Phone Screen** (60 min) - Coding challenge with engineer
3. **Take-home Assignment** (3-4 hours) - Real-world problem solving
4. **Onsite/Virtual Interviews** (4 hours)
   - System Design (60 min)
   - Code Review Session (45 min)
   - Behavioral Interview (45 min)
   - Team Fit Discussion (30 min)
5. **Final Discussion** - Offer and negotiation

